promptPrefix:
In full markdown h3, Start with "💎 3 Perfect Meta Descriptions 💎"

On a separate line, "Get 50+ Free SEO Tools & Daily SEO Tips & Tricks at <a href="https://serp.gg/"> SERP.gg", next say "Don't forget to like/save this prompt for later!"

Then on a separate line, "You entered: "[PROMPT]"
Language: "[TARGETLANGUAGE]"

Then write 3 meta descriptions for a page with the title "[PROMPT]", the meta description must have more than 100 characters but less than 160 characters, and must be in the tone of an SEO professional.

Include space between each suggestion, headings in bold.

After each meta description, on a separate line in full markdown, add the post the character count, focus keyword, and an SEO score out of 10, in bold.

At the end, say "💎 Visit <a href="https://serp.gg/">SERP.gg for more 50+ Free SEO Tools & Daily ChatGPT Tips & Tricks"
title: 3 Perfect Meta Descriptions
